{"tid":2423039,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大生被控無牌管有槍械案控罪書英文版出錯　官促修改","createTime":"2021-02-25T15:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T17:41:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eec6e46926dc930d22f97c267a20fabf92d4624b","tid":2423039,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577562-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577562-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6zJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=675c56e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577562-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=514d4bf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577562-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n一名理工大學學生被控無牌管有槍械、無牌進口戰略物品及管有攻擊性武器，期間粉嶺裁法院裁判官發現控方控罪書的英文版本出錯，表示不希望案件日後有機會在終審法院審訊時，香港法庭會成為外國法庭的笑柄，要求控方修改錯處。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告無牌管有一支胡椒彈手槍、2個胡椒彈彈匣，並在沒有進口許可證下輸入14個防毒面具、3個防毒面具濾芯及一件防彈背心，以及管有2把軍刀和一支伸縮警棍。控方提出案件毋須答辯，並申請將案件押後至4月8日再訊，裁判官陳炳宙指，要先處理控罪書上的英文版本，指控罪書內容寫上「one number Pepper Ball」、「two numbers Pepper Ball」、「14 numbers Respirator」、「 3 numbers canister」。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至4月8日再訊。"},{"pid":"6af0a620ef7a974cf6a668be3a13bdae10a0a91f","tid":2423039,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「one number Pepper Ball」、「two numbers Pepper Ball」、「14 numbers Respirator」、「 3 numbers canister」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDOJ 寫定係警察寫?"},{"pid":"43baab39cdfea70c23eedfed8c7fd85f33b8ed42","tid":2423039,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfec945a379141f54a06f916d0f1281f2fac11a","tid":242